                    h2.mb-5 
                    .subheading.mb-3 Workflow
                    ul.fa-ul.mb-0
                        li
                            span.fa-li
                                i.fas.fa-check
                            | Design-First, Engaging Approach to Shape a Product
                        li
                            span.fa-li
                                i.fas.fa-check
                            | Cross Platform Testing & Debugging
                        li
                            span.fa-li
                                i.fas.fa-check
                            | Cross Functional Teams
                        li
                            span.fa-li
                                i.fas.fa-check
                            | Agile Development & Scrum

            hr.m-0 

